Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:10.93,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up in the morning, brush my teeth and in the blink of an eye, it's 10pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:17.06,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Today also, we laughed a whole lot; we had a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:23.36,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,With my friends, I played the fool, and we all played around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:28.95,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the blood began to run, we wished it was a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:35.83,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't talk about the first time, it wouldn't be in-character.
