Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Earth round?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do rockets fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do magnets pull against each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything in this world can be proven by science.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things that may be eliminated...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiritual phenomena such as a world after death, ghosts and ghost stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way those kinds of sleep-inducing things could be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... they can't be. {That's because, they can't be real.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in spiritualists!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using my day off, I spent 8 hours going one-way to Mt. Osore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting closer to the summit, the beating of my heart increases.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if a spiritualist really exists here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she would live alone here. {they?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have her summon something already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Please summon some soap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bubble, it's Soap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this sensation of helplessness?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be there's someone called Soap...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's S-S-Soap.{timer got to be careful here cause she says some random b4 she says this...}{around 4:48.75 she's saying this sentance}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... if I keep asking, then eventually a contradiction point will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:04:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the blood type of Soap?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try a simpler person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobunaga... please summon Oda Nobunaga! {http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B9%94%E7%94%B0%E4%BF%A1%E9%95%B7}{lol im a fan of Oda Nobunaga too!}{Oda Nobunaga was just as bad as the rest of the late Sengoku period Daimyo and gets an unfair bad reputation}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rejecting me before even trying to summon him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's old after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has to look after her health.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't scold her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scolding people is not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by knowing that, I should reap what I've sown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Onii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 5000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock Paper Scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how you do it Mai-chan, didn't I just explain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to hit me if you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing, you've got incredible concentration. In a way, it's even more cruel than hitting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. As I've just explained, when you lose you defend, when you win you hit, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now! Why did you hit me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's because I won just then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't now was it, it was just then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the moment! Live for the moment! We're that kind of living thing you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK then, let's do it again. {let's start clear?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock paper scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have zero motivation to play!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much of a clown can you be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my mind... something is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hold on Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-chan, w-what's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I carved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god! I thought it had been reincarnated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will put this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, she looks really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah well that doesn't matter, let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, rock paper scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-Mai-chan. That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...rockscispaper...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, such a brutal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, Mai-chan, that doesn't count, that doesn't count. Rockscispaper doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, hitting with the Buddha doesn't count either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, let's do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First comes rock{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock paper scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, that! That's it Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you can do it if you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, let's do the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First comes rock{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why did you hit me?! You did it properly just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I say it, because I don't want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take a look at your Maitreya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll be going to the library to return the books!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you look after the house, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Nano's daruma only has one eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! If I give it another eye I might get praised!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might say 'it's OK to eat as many snacks as you like'!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might've made a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Nano's, so what do I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! She might get mad at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get any snacks for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... here... and here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sakamoto, what should I do? This...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? What were you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, it didn't have an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, try doing what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sakamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sakamoto-san, you're going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late because it took me some time to choose some new books to borrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, what's with that stomach of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not 'ehehe'!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It'll be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no no, that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be born! It'll be born! It'll be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is this some kind of game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No it's not! Your little brother is about to be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-chan, Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play Kokkuri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I'll briefly explain it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First you need to prepare a piece of paper by drawing a gate in the middle like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you write 'yes', 'no' and the 50 Japanese syllabary on the page.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although in some regions, you're supposed to draw a fried tofu on the paper instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's just keep it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for Kokkuri-san to be able to come in, you open the north-facing window. {Then, to invite the Kokkuri-san in, you open the north-facing window.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you set this 10-yen coin on the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We put both of our fingers on it and ask a question that you want to know about,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,such as a person's secret, or who someone likes, or something that's bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, all by itself, the 10-yen coin will move and Kokkuri-san will answer your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some taboos though...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, don't do it by yourself... second, don't mess around when doing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or else you will be haunted by spirits...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if you stop halfway through, you will be haunted, so be wary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty dangerous game, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why don't you give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaaaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... well that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow we have a mini-test, so everyone please study for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Postpone it, postpone it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't the outcome be exactly the same for you no matter how long it's postponed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurai-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Aioi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... about the test we had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... That's a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:16:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not the answer. I'm talking about this thing that looks like it'd vanish pretty easily... did you draw it, Sensei?{no idea some thing kiesou?}{As good as I can figure}{ニフラムで消えそうなキャラの絵を描いて}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I thought that if I included some pictures, the test might be a little easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You draw very interesting pictures, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm bad at drawing pictures, so it was hard to understand wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you include a picture that I've drawn next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw something really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, listen. My picture's going to be in the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei said she'll put them in. {Sensei's going to put it in.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you draw something right now, she'll definitely put yours in, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'definitely', but it's still 'maybe'?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... you're not going to draw something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine. I'll pass on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I have to return this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! One cool guy{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwah! He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aioi-san, you're so good at drawing. You have my respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not that good... I'm awesome at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, his name is Samidare George.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's even cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, what you'd call cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off!{Also spoken at around this point, in a male voice}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwah! Amazing! It's just like a manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naganohara-san, do you draw manga or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, well, only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Please show me next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it. Please show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... ah... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine are much cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just ripped off mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't rip it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you {\i1}did{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of rip-off is known as homage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just admitted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwah! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything works for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses!{That reminds me of Houjou Souun from Sengoku Rance}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An intelligent and cool look that appeals to all women of any era!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is his eyesight bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should just wear contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two just don't get it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll do... this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're underneath his ears!{Referring to the glasses}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, this is a rip-off too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk, tsk, tsk... they're sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwah! So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're OK with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... how about this? A butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From picking you up to serving you tea... you'll feel like a real lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel the magic of Darjeeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses again? I'm sorry, I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't listen to my advice about contacts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-chan, you don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, what's really cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, hold on... this... it's running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwah! It looks so fast and cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it in a normal way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew this while I was listening to jazz music.{also written on-screen}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Sensei, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll hand out this morning's mini-test, so please pass them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to keep secret the fact that I draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I drew a picture like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, even though I lost control, only going to that level was a blessing amongst all the misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty close.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukko's going to tease me for two or three days though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! I have to keep my chin up and move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-sensei, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you, I'm onomatopoeia!{start it after the gibberish}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help but say 'Cock-a-doodle-do' in Japanese even though it's not Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next Nichijou is the sixth. Look forward to it.
